➜湖北诗人木子： 五绝·流歌（外一首|）
http://www.sohu.com/a/417543703_100115135	40776
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200910/2c14fb0235b446cca842d5bdf376c0aa.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝·流歌</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/木子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">客在他乡处，孤城独影飘。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">根深牵故里，何日把君邀?</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200910/d6c15548c93e4847bdc7930d099995bf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·流年一梦</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/木子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">舟行水上骤然停，莫扰空中雁造形。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">似水流年终一梦，红尘一别细叮咛。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200910/952755d5737346e1a7e78154069d54ca.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
