➜湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：处以秋天模式（外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/417545978_100115135	41609
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200910/80458e6d6e494c35a7a7a563e11b614e.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>处以秋天模式</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣(武汉)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花开花落不为争艳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清水池塘里与共成长</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不减情深。前进一万里或两万里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">似爬过沟坎的草</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">迎风、沐雨、披霜，依然挽手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一生叶上绿，岁月纸上骄</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>云淡风轻。行在路上</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>相守以秋天模式</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>太阳下，露珠笑里有欢快回眸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>月下 桂花吐香飘雪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不折叠彼此，好姐妹在心里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>豢养长青树，岁月静好</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">写于2020年9月9日上午</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200910/54b616c2956f4771a62074147882c6cc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
